{"tid":498012,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"他買比特幣4萬贏到900萬！為何呼籲不要再追？ (16:17)","createTime":"2017-12-13T11:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T11:48:11.000Z","uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dd02fb33ae3c650bf3451b7c45bb62797bfea6ba","tid":498012,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:28:13.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=ZWeSRS2AzZMtAPOpxiHhOfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6345d694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】外國傳媒報道，美國白手興家富豪、Millennial Money創辦人Grant Sabatier表示，在2013年開始投資虛擬貨幣「龍頭」比特幣，涉及資金約5,000美元(約3.9萬港元)，當時比特幣價格約72美元，現時他持有大約69.2個比特幣。<br />\n<br />\n他透露，在2011年時首次聽到比特幣，但沒有立即投資，直至在網上看到有關虛擬貨幣的資料後，才決定購買，視為長線投資，當時買入資金約佔整體身家少於1%。Sabatier表示，投資當然是想賺錢，但因投資額不大，一旦輸清也不會影響生活。<br />\n<br />\n由於比特幣愈升愈有，現時升至大約16,600美元，令Sabatier持有比特幣的總值增至114萬美元(約896萬港元)，但他不建議人們現時追入。<br />\n<br />\nSabatier的理由很簡單，就是回憶自己白手興家的歷程，最窮的時候戶口只剩2.26美元(約17港元)，之後靠不斷儲蓄及買股票投資，5年後銀行戶口才有100萬美元(約780萬港元)，但比特幣1年內就做到此效果，這不會穩固。<br />\n<br />\nSabateir再分享，決定一個人未來可賺多少錢，或賺到第一桶金的時間，取決於今日自己的「價值」，但很多人都低估了自己的價值。他勸年輕人要努力，世上沒有「快錢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171213/20171213161751fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20171213%2F20171213161751fi.html&d=ZWeSRS2AzZMtAPOpxiHhOfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=99162fe3\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171213/20171213161751fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"3c641961e4df79ccdcc9ac6286989e7f56f6d3a1","tid":498012,"uid":1067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:31:28.000Z","msg":"火撩陰呢？"},{"pid":"69160315a7d7ef964d4246eaff902696c4fc6913","tid":498012,"uid":2333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"5年搵780萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n投咩資呀  倫敦金？"},{"pid":"837fc89bd6d09b184a493f4c3fef389e313a8890","tid":498012,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>火撩陰呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯，類似火尿深故事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826f82199dc19434fd6c7d41bbcef2c4e6df20f7","tid":498012,"uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"5年就有780萬<br />\n賣屎忽呀"},{"pid":"4b922b198e616f610c0ddd1ff95ae7b02165c679","tid":498012,"uid":106340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:35:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc772dfd950738e4b8a46f85b4bf6cfd27f7f0aa","tid":498012,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:36:35.000Z","msg":"4千幾買100粒 <br />\n幾個月都執幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bcbbce9de4b16f3dc1c726fc4e8a74cb15046d","tid":498012,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T11:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4千幾買100粒 <br />\n幾個月都執幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係錢搵錢既極致"}]}